[{"id": 298, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Vanish</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You were never quite where they thought.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an enemy declares an attack against you, play this card. The attack lands on nothing. Enter <strong>Hidden</strong> and move to any unoccupied position within reach.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The attacker is <strong>Exposed</strong> until the start of their next turn.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Gain 1 <strong>Notoriety</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 299, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Find the Gap</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Every lock has a mechanism.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Investigation</strong> check. On success:</div><div class=\"co\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"ql\"><div class=\"qi\">What is the fastest way through this obstacle?</div><div class=\"qi\">What is being deliberately kept from view here?</div><div class=\"qi\">Who here cannot afford to have you proceed?</div></div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Ask one additional question.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 300, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Sneak Attack</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You weren't watching the right shadow.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Stealth</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> a target that is unaware of you or occupied with an ally.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> <strong>Hide</strong> nearby.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 301, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Cheap Shot</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Fair fights are for people with something to prove.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Acrobatics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> a target from an unexpected angle \u2014 they are <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is also <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 302, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Shadowstep</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Distance is a suggestion.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Stealth</strong> check. On success, <strong>Move</strong> instantly to any unoccupied position in the <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 you arrive <strong>Hidden</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span><strong>Strike</strong> immediately on arrival.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 303, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Distract</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Their attention is a resource. You just spent it.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Deception</strong> check. On success, a target's attention is fully on you \u2014 all other creatures in the <strong>Scene</strong> gain a <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> die on their next <strong>Action</strong> this beat.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 304, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Exploit Opening</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You were waiting for exactly that.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally applies any negative condition to a target, perform an <strong>Acrobatics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> that target immediately.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Apply <strong>Exposed</strong> or <strong>Rooted</strong> as well.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 305, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Slip Away</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You were already leaving.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When targeted by an attack or hostile <strong>Action</strong>, perform an <strong>Acrobatics</strong> check. On success, the <strong>Action</strong> misses \u2014 <strong>Move</strong> to an adjacent position.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Attacker is <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 306, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Read the Mark</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You size up a target before they know you're looking.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Perception</strong> check. On success:</div><div class=\"co\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"ql\"><div class=\"qi\">What is this person trying to hide right now?</div><div class=\"qi\">What would make them flinch?</div><div class=\"qi\">Where are they most exposed?</div></div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Ask one additional question.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 307, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">In the Shadows</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: you are unseen.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, you remain <strong>Hidden</strong> between turns. Any <strong>Strike</strong> you make from this state gains a <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> die.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Remain <strong>Hidden</strong> after striking.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 308, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Case the Scene</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You spend thirty seconds doing what others spend an hour missing.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Investigation</strong> check. On success, name one escape route, one hidden object, or one person in this <strong>Scene</strong> the GM has not yet mentioned \u2014 it exists.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Name a second true thing.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 309, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Cunning Strike</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The injury is secondary. The message is the point.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Sleight of Hand</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> a target and choose one: deal damage, or forgo damage to apply a condition \u2014 <strong>Rattled</strong>, <strong>Exposed</strong>, or <strong>Rooted</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Deal damage AND apply the condition.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 310, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Smoke and Mirrors</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Let them argue about what they saw.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Deception</strong> check. On success, create a false impression \u2014 a sound, a silhouette, a dropped object. Every enemy in the <strong>Scene</strong> is <strong>Rattled</strong> until one of them spends an <strong>Action</strong> investigating.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Two enemies investigate, not one.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 311, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Vanishing Strike</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">One moment, a blade. The next, nothing.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Stealth</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> from <strong>Hidden</strong> \u2014 then immediately re-enter <strong>Hidden</strong> in a new position.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is <strong>Exposed</strong> before you vanish.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 312, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Eldritch Strike</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The power is yours. So is the price.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Remove a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> from your pool and <strong>Strike</strong> at any range \u2014 add that die to your strike. On success, the target is <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Regain the spent <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span>.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target loses their next defensive <strong>Action</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 313, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Siphon</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You take something they needed.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Spellcast</strong> check. On success, name one thing a target has \u2014 composure, <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span>, momentum, leverage \u2014 and remove it.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> equal to what was removed.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 314, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Hex</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Bad luck has a name. Right now it's theirs.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Spellcast</strong> check. On success, curse a target \u2014 until the <strong>Scene</strong> ends, every <strong>Action</strong> they take costs them something extra. The GM decides what.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> You name the cost instead of the GM \u2014 it holds for the rest of the <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 315, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Dark Grasp</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Distance is irrelevant. They're already in your grip.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Spellcast</strong> check. On success, <strong>Restrain</strong> a target at any range \u2014 they are <strong>Rooted</strong>. The grip holds until they break it.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 316, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Feed the Fire</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">More. Always more.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Remove a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> from your pool. Perform a <strong>Spellcast</strong> check \u2014 add that die to the roll. On success, your next <strong>Act</strong> this <strong>Scene</strong> resolves without interruption or resistance, and gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> <strong>Draw</strong> 1 after that <strong>Act</strong> resolves.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 317, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Terrify</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">They see what your patron sees in you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Intimidation</strong> check. On success, reveal something of your true power \u2014 all enemies who witness it are <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One target flees entirely.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 318, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Misdirection</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">That's not what they think they saw.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally would be targeted, perform a <strong>Deception</strong> check. On success, the <strong>Action</strong> redirects to a target of your choice within the <strong>Scene</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Redirected target is also <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 319, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Drain Life</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Their loss is your survival.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Spellcast</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> a target \u2014 recover one lost <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> for every <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> they lose from this strike.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Also gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 320, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Shadow Step</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The dark knows where you want to go.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Remove a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> from your pool. <strong>Move</strong> instantly to any shadow or dim area in the <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 no check required. Arrive <strong>Hidden</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span><strong>Strike</strong> immediately on arrival.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 321, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Hungering Darkness</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: something follows them now.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, one named target in the <strong>Scene</strong> is pursued by an unseen force \u2014 you pierce their <strong>Hidden</strong> and any concealment.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also <strong>Rattled</strong> at <strong>Scene</strong> start.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 322, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Whisper of Ruin</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You don't threaten. You inform.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Intimidation</strong> check. On success, speak a truth about what awaits a target if they continue. They must immediately choose: stand down, or continue with <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> If they continue, they are also <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 323, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Curse of Weakness</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">They can still fight. Just not as well.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Spellcast</strong> check. On success, a target's next <strong>Action</strong> automatically produces a lesser result than intended \u2014 the GM determines the diminishment.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Effect lasts for two <strong>Actions</strong>, not one.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 324, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Patron's Favor</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">They intervene. The cost comes later.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When you fail a check, remove a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> from your pool \u2014 your patron turns the failure into a success. The GM adds a <strong>Debt</strong> token.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Success becomes exceptional \u2014 GM treats as a crit.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 325, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Void Sight</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You see through things that don't want to be seen through.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Perception</strong> check. On success:</div><div class=\"co\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"ql\"><div class=\"qi\">What in this <strong>Scene</strong> is concealed or disguised?</div><div class=\"qi\">What here does not belong?</div><div class=\"qi\">What is the most dangerous thing in this <strong>Scene</strong>?</div></div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Ask one additional question.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 326, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Speak to the Ground</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The land remembers everything.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success:</div><div class=\"co\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"ql\"><div class=\"qi\">What happened in this place recently?</div><div class=\"qi\">What is approaching that hasn't arrived yet?</div><div class=\"qi\">What is this place protecting?</div></div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Ask one additional question.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 327, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Root &amp; Hold</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The earth does what you ask.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, a target is <strong>Rooted</strong> in place.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> A second target is also <strong>Rooted</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 328, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Living Ground</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The terrain has a side.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, claim a section of the <strong>Scene</strong> as living terrain \u2014 allies moving through it are <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span>; enemies moving through it are <strong>Rooted</strong> for one beat.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Terrain persists into the next <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 329, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Wild Shape</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You stop pretending to be one thing.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, take the shape of any creature you have encountered \u2014 gain its movement and <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on <strong>Actions</strong> that creature would excel at.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Gain the creature's natural armor as <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 330, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Entangle</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The plants have opinions about your enemies.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, vines, roots, or debris grab every enemy in an area \u2014 all are <strong>Rooted</strong> until they break free.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Breaking free costs them their next <strong>Action</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 331, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Mend</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Growth is the nature of living things.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, touch an ally \u2014 they recover one lost <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> as the world around you briefly blooms.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Remove one condition from them also.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> A second ally nearby also recovers a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 332, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Thornwall</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Nature doesn't warn. It responds.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an enemy moves toward you or an ally, perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, thorns or growth erupts \u2014 the enemy is <strong>Rooted</strong> and takes the consequences of moving into sharp terrain.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> All enemies who witness hesitate \u2014 <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}]